# Add psychological-operations launch-arg switches.
#
# Declares three command-line switches in components/psyops/:
#   --psyop=<name>        names the psyop bound to this session
#   --x-app               flags this as the master X-app (root) session
#   --config-base-dir=<p> base directory for state (required)
#
# Adds early-startup validation in ChromeMainDelegate::BasicStartupComplete()
# that fails the browser process if --config-base-dir is missing or if
# neither --psyop nor --x-app is provided. Subprocesses are exempt (they
# inherit their parent's command line; the gate is a one-shot at the
# browser-process startup boundary).
#
# This patch only registers and validates the switches; it does not yet
# wire them into any session behavior.

--- /dev/null
+++ b/components/psyops/BUILD.gn
@@ -0,0 +1,14 @@
